{"tid":2197384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"漁護署利用環控水耕技術栽培車厘茄、士多啤梨和菠菜","createTime":"2020-09-10T14:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:57:25.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cf4daedf18983c6e66f2d153eb53e156927341","tid":2197384,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"漁護署利用環控水耕技術栽培車厘茄、士多啤梨和菠菜<br />\n2020-09-10 HKT 21:18<br />\n<br />\n&quot;漁護署與全環水控研發中心成功利用環控水耕技術，栽培多種非時令蔬果，包括：車厘茄、士多啤梨和菠菜。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署農業管理主任王灝雲說，以室內全環控水耕場種植便可不受季節所限，可以不斷採收，以應對全年的需求，長遠發展可以穩定本地非時令蔬果的供應和確保作物的品質......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548959-20200910.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548959-20200910.htm&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=2ec2334b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548959-20200910.htm&h=238e33d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548959-20200910.htm</a>"},{"pid":"92dcfb721196777dff8b2dbb41bdf52905aca6b3","tid":2197384,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b241612e750c2223433051793f0a867a3c815cd","tid":2197384,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"諗起農業，就諗起淡水....<br />\n<br />\n香港一日唔獨立，一日都唔會整海水化淡廠，但明明個個香港人都想要"},{"pid":"db736ebbb4cc00dd474c1182bd1488a2516f0b5a","tid":2197384,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b241612e750c2223433051793f0a867a3c815cd","tid":2197384,"uid":21699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"諗起農業，就諗起淡水....<br />\n<br />\n香港一日唔獨立，一日都唔會整海水化淡廠，但明明個個香港人都想要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa